title: Hour 2 - Kevin Durant Stuck in Jersey, Gronk Retired, Brian Windhorst
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Kevin Durant Stuck in Jersey, Gronk Retired, Brian Windhorst
description:
Dan talks about the progress (or lack thereof) of Kevin Durant's trade request and Rob Gronkowski's retirement status. And he talks to Brian Windhorst about KD and the rest of the NBA player movement.
